      "en": ["Museum of Fine Arts Ghent - <p>The original TIFF files of this work, in highest resolution and color-coded, can be ordered from <a href=\"https://artinflanders.be/nl/kunst/zelfportret-studie\" target=\"_blank\">meemoo</a>. If this image is used for a printed publication or a commercial product, Museum of Fine Arts Ghent would appreciate having 2 copies sent to Fernand Scribedreef 1, B-9000 Gent.</p>"]
